# 🔄 CI/CD Pipeline

The Azure DevOps pipeline consists of two stages.

## Stage 1 — Build

* Checkout source code
* Build Docker image
* Push image to Azure Container Registry

## Stage 2 — Deploy

* Connect to AKS Cluster
* Apply Kubernetes manifests
* Deploy application
* Expose service through Azure Load Balancer

## Successful Pipeline Execution

### Build Stage

![Pipeline Build](screenshots/pipeline-success-2.png)

### Deploy Stage

![Pipeline Deploy](screenshots/pipeline-success-2.1.png)

